59","tid":589042,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"我都係百萬富翁 周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801956e80d7b6e872b590c0f804c75dd03a9c201","tid":589042,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:47:12.000Z","msg":"10. 香港不適用"},{"pid":"16f2807e52a93b0daae77fd9ab10db5d009c55b3","tid":589042,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"11.做到除(10.)外以上各點"},{"pid":"7e7a6b9eba87b63c4c7edad7303f80c2776af55f","tid":589042,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:52:24.000Z","msg":"11 參透實戰理論"}]}